'''泥灘地浪人'''（{{lang-en|The Muddy Basin Ramblers}}）是一個由一群熱愛[[台灣|台灣]]並定居於當地的[[美國人|美國]]與[[英國人|英國籍]]人士組成於[[2002年|2002年]]的[[街頭藝人|街頭]][[流行樂團|樂隊]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/feat/archives/2014/12/19/2003607066|title=Muddy Basin Ramblers celebrate Christmas - Taipei Times|accessdate=2017-02-24|work=www.taipeitimes.com|archive-date=2019-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190827100450/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/feat/archives/2014/12/19/2003607066|dead-url=no}}</ref>。泥灘地浪人的主要風格源自{{link-en|克難樂隊|Jug Band}}、[[藍調|藍調民謠]]、[[爵士乐|傳統爵士]]以及[[搖擺樂|搖擺樂]]<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=https://blow.streetvoice.com/18269-%E7%94%A8-swing-%E8%AE%93%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E7%9C%8B%E8%A6%8B%E5%8F%B0%E5%8C%97-%E6%B3%A5%E7%81%98%E5%9C%B0%E6%B5%AA%E4%BA%BA%E6%94%B9%E7%B7%A8%E5%8F%B0%E8%AA%9E%E7%B6%93%E5%85%B8%E3%80%88%E8%B7%B3/|title=用 Swing 讓大家看見台北 泥灘地浪人改編台語經典〈跳舞時代〉 - Blow 吹音樂|date=2016-02-28|newspaper=Blow 吹音樂|accessdate=2017-02-24|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2019-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202091325/https://blow.streetvoice.com/18269-%e7%94%a8-swing-%e8%ae%93%e5%a4%a7%e5%ae%b6%e7%9c%8b%e8%a6%8b%e5%8f%b0%e5%8c%97-%e6%b3%a5%e7%81%98%e5%9c%b0%e6%b5%aa%e4%ba%ba%e6%94%b9%e7%b7%a8%e5%8f%b0%e8%aa%9e%e7%b6%93%e5%85%b8%e3%80%88%e8%b7%b3/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，其特色為作品經常脫胎於各種經典樂曲，並以數種自製樂器混合演奏。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/feat/archives/2015/02/02/2003610619|title=Muddy Basin Ramblers Grammy bound - Taipei Times|accessdate=2017-02-24|work=www.taipeitimes.com|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128034544/http://www.taipeitimes.com/News/feat/archives/2015/02/02/2003610619|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://blow.streetvoice.com/6304-%E6%B3%A5%E7%81%98%E5%9C%B0%E6%B5%AA%E4%BA%BA-%E8%91%AB%E8%98%86%E8%A3%A1%E8%B3%A3%E7%9A%84%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E8%97%A5%EF%BC%9F/|title=泥灘地浪人 葫蘆裡賣的是什麼藥？ - Blow 吹音樂|date=2015-01-11|newspaper=Blow 吹音樂|accessdate=2017-02-24|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327070047/https://blow.streetvoice.com/6304-%e6%b3%a5%e7%81%98%e5%9c%b0%e6%b5%aa%e4%ba%ba-%e8%91%ab%e8%98%86%e8%a3%a1%e8%b3%a3%e7%9a%84%e6%98%af%e4%bb%80%e9%ba%bc%e8%97%a5%ef%bc%9f/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://reading.gov.taipei/ct.asp?xItem=127110268&CtNode=84572&mp=100021|title=大稻埕國際藝術節初登板 ／在地老外+日台相聲+跨界合體|accessdate=2017-02-24|date=2015-10-20|last=曾婷|work=reading.gov.taipei|language=zh-hant|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170225051442/http://reading.gov.taipei/ct.asp?xItem=127110268&CtNode=84572&mp=100021|archive-date=2017-02-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.alive.com.tw/Life/0055/Gallery-ARTL000063734.html|title=賣藥秀民謠  致敬三零年代|accessdate=2017-02-24|work=alive Taiwan - 品味生活究極誌|archive-date=2017-12-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171226152657/http://www.alive.com.tw/Life/0055/Gallery-ARTL000063734.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

